Program: Outlook
Title: Defining Respect
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03kbr9p
Last Broadcast Date: Not available
Discussing respect and how much is enough. Programme begins with a look at the affects of the worst floods in Mosambique in 50 years. Also, the life of Tajikistani composer Ziyodullo Shakhidi and his family who have a mission to save the traditional music of central Asia. Finally, the magic of the Northern Lights in the Arctic Circle. Presenter: Behrouz Afagh. Show less